scenario_text: Reduce the number of available vehicles from 2 to 1 to test the feasibility of serving all customers with a single vehicle.
Increase the demand at customer location 4 from 9 to 20 to test the impact on vehicle capacity and route feasibility.
"Introduce a time window constraint for customer location 6, requiring service between 10:00 AM and 12:00 PM, to evaluate its impact on route feasibility and total distance."
"Introduce a constraint that requires customer locations 3, 7, and 10 to be served consecutively by the same vehicle to evaluate the impact on route feasibility and total distance."
"Increase the demand at customer locations 5, 6, and 11 by 50% to test the impact on vehicle capacity utilization and route feasibility."
"Introduce a constraint that requires customer locations 2, 5, and 8 to be served by separate vehicles to evaluate the impact on vehicle utilization and route feasibility."

"Introduce a constraint that requires customer locations 1, 4, and 9 to be served by the same vehicle to evaluate the impact on route feasibility and total distance given their diverse demand and distance from each other."
